.service.service-massage
  h1.service-title Massage

  .service-container.service-container--closed
    svg.service-image(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg', xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink', viewbox='0 0 1920 500', preserveaspectratio='xMidYMid slice')
      defs
        clippath#massagePath
          // r = 992 = hyp = Math.sqrt(960*960+250*250)
          circle.clip(cx='960', cy='250', r='992')

      image(clip-path='url(#massagePath)', width='1920', height='500', xlink:href='img/massage.jpg')

    .service-content
      .grid
        .service-body
          i.service-action.fa.fa-times

          .service-caption
            h2.service-caption-title Massage Therapy

            .service-caption-description
              p.
                Whether your need is to have a moment of relaxation, reduce muscle tension
                or attain relief from chronic pain, a theraputic massage can enhance your
                overall sense of emotional &amp; physical well being..

              p.
                Let your worries &amp; stresses face away as soon as you enter our
                treatment rooms. With mood lighting, deep soothing music &amp;
                electronic heated massage couch.

              p.mt.
                Choose from our range of massage treatments all carried out by our
                passionate &amp; highly experienced therapists.

          .service-copy
            .alert.alert-info
              h2.alert-title Benefits of Massage Therapy
              p.alert-content.
                Massage therapy is more than relaxing me-time. Studies continue to prove the physical, and emotional benefits of even a single massage therapy session. As the number of proven health benefits grows, so do the number of Americans who turn to Massage Envy for a more balanced lifestyle. In fact, we've provided over 50 million therapeutic massages nationwide. That's a lot of happy, healthy customers.

              a.btn.btn-info--inverse(href="#service-massage-benefits") Learn More..

            include massage-benefits

            .row.service-copy-section
              .cell-sm-auto.mr
                img.service-copy-image(src='img/massage-deep-tissue.jpg', title='Deep Tissue Massage', alt='Deep Tissue Massage')

              .cell-sm
                h2.service-copy-section-title Deep Tissue Massage

                .service-copy-section-content
                  .row
                    .cell-sm.mr
                      p.
                        The massage focuses on releving tension &amp; aching muscles. The
                        fundamental elements of the deep tissue muscle massage are experienced
                        in deep presure using blended massage oils.

                      p.mt.
                        Tailor made to suit the individual needs of the client.

                    .cell-sm-3
                      h2.service-offer-title 1 hour £35.00
                      span.service-offer-subtitle Introductory price £25.00 and £20 for 1/2hour

            .row.service-copy-section
              .cell-sm-auto.mr
                img.service-copy-image(src="img/massage-hot-stone.jpg", title="Hot Stone Massage", alt="Hot Stone Massage")

              .cell-sm
                h2.service-copy-section-title Relaxing Full Body Massage

                .service-copy-section-content
                  .row
                    .cell-sm.mr
                      p.
                        After consultation to find out your specific needs, the therapist will use carefully
                        applied pressures to stimulate the nervous system, to relieve the muscle tension and
                        encourage healthy circulation to disolve away all your stress and tensions.

                      p.mt.
                        Relaxes your body, mind and spirit.

                    .cell-sm-3
                      h2.service-offer-title 1 hour £35.00
                      span.service-offer-subtitle Introductory price £25.00

            .row.service-copy-section
              .cell-sm-auto.mr
                img.service-copy-image(src="img/massage-hot-stone.jpg", title="Hot Stone Massage", alt="Hot Stone Massage")

              .cell-sm
                h2.service-copy-section-title Hot Stone Therapy Massage

                .service-copy-section-content
                  .row
                    .cell-sm.mr
                      p.
                        Smooth hot stones are placed on chakra points of the body them
                        massaged allowing the therapist to access deeper muscle layers, melts
                        away tension, eases muscle stiffness &amp; increases circulation and
                        metabolism.

                      p.mt.
                        The volcanic stones are believed to promote relaxation and healing, as
                        well as eliminating negative energy withing the body, mind &amp; soul.

                    .cell-sm-3
                      h2.service-offer-title 1 hour £35.00
                      span.service-offer-subtitle Introductory price £25.00

            .row.service-copy-section
              .cell-sm-auto.mr
                img.service-copy-image(src="img/massage-mother-to-be.jpg", title="Mother to be Massage", alt="Mother to be Massage")

              .cell-sm
                h2.service-copy-section-title Mother to be Massage

                .service-copy-section-content
                  .row
                    .cell-sm.mr
                      p.
                        Massage therapy during pregnancy is a healthy way to reduce stress and
                        promote overall welness.

                      p.mt.
                        It can also relieve many of the normal discomoforts experienced during
                        pregnancy, such as backaches, stiff neck, leg cramps, headeaches and
                        swelling. Taior made to suit the individual needs of the client.

                    .cell-sm-3
                      h2.service-offer-title 1 hour £35.00
                      span.service-offer-subtitle Introductory price £25.00
